      "span_text": "Likewise,  observe that at the University of North Carolina, Chapel Hill, \"even the more intuitive library services and resources, to say nothing of these difficultto-use ones, were almost invisible from the Blackboard course page\" (p. 84), and recommend organizing resources to correspond to specific courses and assignments.",
